{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过实验</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究活动，知道电磁铁的磁性强弱与</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电流</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大小和线圈匝数的关系</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电流磁效应。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">匝铁钉、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">匝铁钉、开关、电源、电流表、滑动变阻器、曲别针</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.设计实验</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和进行实验</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步骤</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用漆包线</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">绕</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">匝</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的电磁铁</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">连接</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到电路中，断开开关，观察电磁铁吸引</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">曲别针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的情况，并将</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">曲别针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的数目记录在表格中。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步骤</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">闭合开关，观察电磁铁</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吸引曲别针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的情况</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">接着</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">断开开关，观察铁钉是否还</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吸引</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">曲别针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步骤</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：移动滑动</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">变阻器滑片，使电路中电流逐渐增大，观察每次电流增大时电磁铁吸引</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">曲别针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数目的变化</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步骤</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：把用漆包线</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">绕</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">匝</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的电磁铁</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">另外一个</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用漆包线</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">绕</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">100<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">匝</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的电磁铁</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">串联接入电路，闭合开关，观察两个电磁铁吸引</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">曲别针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的数目</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">并分别记录在表格中。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">接着</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">断开开关，观察</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">两个</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">铁钉是否还</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吸引</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">曲别针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.分析与论证：</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）观察</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步骤</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实验现象，可以得出电磁铁磁性的有无</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">由</span></span><u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</u><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通断</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">来控制。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）分析</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步骤</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实验数据可知，在线圈</span></span><u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</u><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相同</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的情况下，</span></span><u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</u><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">越大</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其磁性越强。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）分析</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步骤</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实验数据可知，在</span></span><u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</u><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相同</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的情况下，</span></span><u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</u><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">越多</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，电磁铁的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">磁性</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">越强。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电磁铁磁性的有无</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">由开关通断</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">来控制</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；匝数一定时</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通入的电流越大</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其磁性越强</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电流相同</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的情况下，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">匝数越多</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，电磁铁的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">磁性</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">越强</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.该实验利用了控制变量法进行探究；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.电磁继电器利用电磁铁进行控制。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}